      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what do u mean by \"goblin math\"? i thought you were a financial advisor. i'm just trying to understand the actual math behind the interest accrual and the principal reduction. can u just explain the actual calculation without the metaphors?",
      "source": "evaluator"
